title: Adshel launches national digital network
text:
Adshel launches national digital network Adshel launches national digital network Next Story Prev Story 3 hrs ago Read more: Canberra Times 
APN News & Media's outdoor advertising business Adshel will next week launch a new digital network with 270 screens across five Australian capital cities. Adshel, which is also part owned by Clear Channel International, will on October 5 launch its new network in Sydney, Melbourne, Brisbane, Adelaide and Perth, with advertisers including telecommunications, financial, travel and luxury companies.   Canberra Times.
